/reason.com/people/elizabeth-nolan-brown/" title="Posts by Elizabeth Nolan Brown" class="author url fn" rel="author">Elizabeth Nolan Brown</a> </span> <span class="pipe">|</span> <time class="updated" datetime="2019-04-16T15:25:10-04:00">4.16.2019 3:25 PM</time></p><div class="rcom-social-tools"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2019%2F04%2F16%2Fare-socialists-more-like-libertarians-than-wed-like-to-admit%2F" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--facebook" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Facebook" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2019%2F04%2F16%2Fare-socialists-more-like-libertarians-than-wed-like-to-admit%2F&text=Are+socialists+more+like+libertarians+than+they%27d+like+to+admit%3F&via=reason" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--twitter" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Twitter" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a><a href="https://www.reddit.com/submit?url=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2019%2F04%2F16%2Fare-socialists-more-like-libertarians-than-wed-like-to-admit%2F&title=Are+socialists+more+like+libertarians+than+they%27d+like+to+admit%3F" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--reddit" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Reddit" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-reddit"></i></a><a href="mailto:?subject=Shared+From+Reason.com%3A+Are+socialists+more+like+libertarians+than+they%27d+like+to+admit%3F&body=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2019%2F04%2F16%2Fare-socialists-more-like-libertarians-than-wed-like-to-admit%2F" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--email" data-ga-click="true"